推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=003d2f8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"bbc3e951fde9b3064b9b64d32c1302e18eea1336","tid":1570150,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"有冇佢既channel"},{"pid":"aff81a10861d1e92c20a894fe3b16cdbfb635852","tid":1570150,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"}]}